    "## Task 3: Model Development\n",
    "1. Transform the input feature using Polynomial Features (Degree = 3).\n",
    "2. Train a Polynomial Regression model.\n",
    "3. Predict salaries for the test dataset."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
